An Unlikely Event

I cannot believe you made it here! The chances of you reading these words are astronomically low but yet here you are, reading this paragraph. In order for you to be reading these words, your parents would have had to met and had you as their child. Your parents parents would have to go through the same ordeal and so on. After you have been born, you made several thousands of decisions. Each one of those decisions has now led you here, to my webpage. Life is beautiful and I cannot believe that we exist.

  • Never Cared
  • Another Thing To Do It
  • Sippin Red
  • KTM Drip
  • Tattoo's & Ink
  • Biscotti
